For each dot in the diagram, we can count the number of paths from January 1 to it by adding the number of ways to get to the dots to the left of it, above it, and above and to the left of it, starting from the topmost leftmost dot. This yields the following numbers of paths:
 egin{tabular}{|c|c|c|c|c|c|c|c|c|c|c|c|}
